Product Information

Hey there, lab pros! Are you seeking a formidable upgrade for your fluorescence illumination setup? Look no further - the PRIOR Scientific L200US- Lumen 200 is a top contender! Tested extensively and sporting a 200W fluorescence illuminator, this system nightlights like none other. Its unrivaled, cost-effective magic powers make ordinary 100 Watt mercury and halogen lamphouses pale in comparison. The intense illumination is facilitated by Priors proprietary 2,000-hour-life arc lamp paired with a liquid light guide, minimizing heat transfer for rock-steady results during your time lapse experiments. The Lumen 200 boasts a variable light attenuation control, minimizing risks of bleaching and phototoxicity. Moreover, for those with unique light requirements, the Lumen 220 model - complete with an extended wavelength in UV and IR - is up for grabs. Talk about lighting it up right!

Key Features

200W Fluorescence illuminator

2m liquid light guide included

Variable light attenuation control

Lumen 220 model with extended UV and IR transmission available
